OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fand very warm on Friday, chance of
OL,7,Fshowers in north. The weekend dry and
OL,8,Fwarm with the best of the sunshine
OL,9,Facross Argyll.
